      "raw_text": "During the presidential campaign\nthe question of woman suffrage\nwas much discussed among women\npro and can, and at an afternoon\ntea the conversation turned that\nway between the women guests.\n\n\nAre you a woman suffragist p\nasked the one who was most inter-\nested\n\n\nIndeed, am not\" replied the\nother, most emphatically. T.. 80\n\n\n\"Oh, that's too bad, but just sup\nposing you were, whom would you\nsupport in the present campaign ?\"\n\n\nThe same man I've always sup\nported, of course was the apt re-\nply-\"my husband\""
